{"tid":998250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係呀！就係你呀！世上總要有人勞碌一生下賤生存","createTime":"2019-01-27T23:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T00:21:59.000Z","uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe84172f91bf40e81b92f7d70a20b5f9f2a35304","tid":998250,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:06:17.000Z","msg":"起身預備返工未？<br />\n<br />\n有錢仔呢個時候仲好累<br />\n<br />\n㩜住尋晚岩識既大學生女朋友<br />\n<br />\n回味緊條女唔係大識但又好落力既blow job<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭就係碌架床上隔爬落下層返工"},{"pid":"cac6a55ed289e4e35abc18d9b0ff5287e8e5e305","tid":998250,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:14:12.000Z","msg":"係！<br />\n<br />\n人生就係咁<br />\n<br />\n有錢仔每月由佢家族基金攞既生活費用<br />\n<br />\n比你全家收入夾埋仲要多四倍<br />\n<br />\n但佢都有佢困難<br />\n<br />\n每月最多只可以應付三個女朋友既使用<br />\n<br />\n要照顧四條女？<br />\n<br />\nSorry<br />\n<br />\n真係緊緊夠錢<br />\n<br />\n何況有錢仔覺得太多女朋友會影響佢打網球既時間<br />\n<br />\n佢好有紀律，只限自己同時有三個女朋友"},{"pid":"1b821f0a9690a994e8a68b016a849ed9b1c9d171","tid":998250,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:17:30.000Z","msg":"你條窮撚<br />\n<br />\n每日呃自己話行路身體好<br />\n<br />\n事實上係為左慳4.8既搭車錢<br />\n<br />\n行路返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每逢一至五日日行<br />\n<br />\n為慳4.8日日吸馬路廢氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你條命真係好撚下賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f539392622d93e914d748637ff54285cc7d0f85","tid":998250,"uid":78683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:27:28.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"b37dcbc670decefa40639969ffa12a627d2478c6","tid":998250,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:31:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83f3d3b054edb561684b949e1f90dd63dd25616b","tid":998250,"uid":64244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T23:32:53.000Z","msg":"屈蛇寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces